    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_9_2732-2847",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2732-2847",
      "markText": "当你开始主动地、有意识地往前走时，不仅你的未来会更好， 你的过去也会更好。过去会越来越成为对 你有意义的事情，而不是你的遭遇。",
      "totalCount": 1328,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2732&rangeEnd=2847",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2732&rangeEnd=2847"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_8_4308-4375",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4308-4375",
      "markText": "未来的你是什么样的人？ 你想象和有意识规划未来的自我的频率是怎样的？",
      "totalCount": 1122,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4308&rangeEnd=4375",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4308&rangeEnd=4375"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_5_3255-3314",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3255-3314",
      "markText": "愿景越具体，路径就越清晰，做事的动力也就越大。选择自己的目标，然后将整个灵魂交给这个目标，你就会在适当的时候实现转变。",
      "totalCount": 1020,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3255&rangeEnd=3314",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3255&rangeEnd=3314"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_7_7143-7182",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7143-7182",
      "markText": "如果你不再削足适履地给自己分类，而是敞开心扉、迎接变化的可能性，那会发生什么？",
      "totalCount": 992,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7143&rangeEnd=7182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7143&rangeEnd=7182"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_8_2735-2801",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2735-2801",
      "markText": "做决策最好是根据未来的自己想要什么，而不是根据现在的自己想要什么。决策与行动时应该站在未来期望情境的制高点上，而不是基于眼前的情况。",
      "totalCount": 924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2801",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2801"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_6_5654-5691",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5654-5691",
      "markText": "那些你抱有最大期许的人往往给你的最少，你抱有最小期许的人反而给你的最多。”",
      "totalCount": 870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5654&rangeEnd=5691",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5654&rangeEnd=5691"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_6_729-753",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "729-753",
      "markText": "人们误以为自己已是成品，而实际上他们只是半成品。",
      "totalCount": 832,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=729&rangeEnd=753",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=729&rangeEnd=753"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_7_2902-2967",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2902-2967",
      "markText": "标签可以服务于目标，但目标不应该服务于标签。当目标服务于标签时，你就让标签成了自己的终极现实，你的生活就是为了证明或支持那个标签。",
      "totalCount": 812,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2902&rangeEnd=2967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2902&rangeEnd=2967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_4_396-446",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "396-446",
      "markText": "在那些改变了自我和人生的人身上只有一件“奇事”，那就是他们一直注视着未来，他们拒绝被自己的过去定义。",
      "totalCount": 714,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=396&rangeEnd=446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_3_6215-6255",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6215-6255",
      "markText": "若无有意义的目标，尝试改变就没有意义。需要动用无以为继的意志力最终将会导致失败。",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6215&rangeEnd=6255",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6215&rangeEnd=6255"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_28_3177-3213",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "3177-3213",
      "markText": "倾听，提出好问题，不要下判断，不要提建议。这些就是共情见证者的关键原则。",
      "totalCount": 690,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3177&rangeEnd=3213",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3177&rangeEnd=3213"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_3_2314-2370",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2314-2370",
      "markText": "这一切贯穿着一个隐含的假定： 你是怎样一个人，是天生的，而且你无法改变它。",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2314&rangeEnd=2370",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2314&rangeEnd=2370"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_3_4697-4765",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4697-4765",
      "markText": "有一个可以退回去的“盒子”会大大减轻情绪的压力——“对呀，我现在觉得不舒服，它肯定不适合我”，哪怕“盒子”会限制你的自由、眼界和创造力。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4697&rangeEnd=4765",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4697&rangeEnd=4765"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_4_828-912",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "828-912",
      "markText": "人们常把过去当作故步自封、拒绝成长的借口。他们也常把过去当作自己之前或将要犯下的过错的借口，就像塞巴斯蒂安那样。但归咎于过去只是在为自己开脱，不负责任，没有个人能动性。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=828&rangeEnd=912",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=828&rangeEnd=912"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015161_11_2091-2182",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2091-2182",
      "markText": "真我并非现在的自己，更不是习以为常的自己。真我是你所最笃信的、最想成为的自己。另外，真我是会变的。本真在于诚实，诚实在于面对真相，而不是因为不想进行艰难的对话就给自己的局限性找理由。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015161&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2091&rangeEnd=2182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9d321b0813ab6c6cg011882?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2091&rangeEnd=2182"
    },
    {
